    Get seasonal forcing

    get_seasonal_forcing.Rd

    Convert Fourier function parameters into a smooth vector of daily seasonal forcing. Used within set_seasonality function

    get_seasonal_forcing(season_params, n_days, floor = 0.001)

    Arguments

    season_params

    List of Fourier function parameters describing seasonality

    n_days

    Numerical value of output vector length

    floor

    Minimum permitted value of output

    Examples

    season_params <- list(g0 = 0.28,
                          g = c(-0.30, -0.03, 0.17),
                          h = c(-0.35, 0.32, -0.08),
                          theta_c = 0.28)
get_seasonal_forcing(season_params,
                      n_days = 1000,
                      floor = 0.005)
